ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Poland- Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take, on behalf of Canada, the measures necessary to BRING INTO FORCE the CONVENTION between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF POLAND for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with Respect to Taxes on Income.
